---
import { PenTool, Send, Sparkles, Clock } from 'lucide-react';
---

<section id="pen-section" class="py-24 bg-neo-red border-t-4 border-black relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-6xl relative z-10">
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            
            <!-- Text Content -->
            <div>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
                    <div class="w-8 h-4 bg-black"></div>
                    <span class="text-black font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm bg-white border-2 border-black px-2">Scriptorium</span>
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-6xl md:text-7xl font-black text-black mb-6 leading-none tracking-tighter drop-shadow-neo">
                    KELİMELERİN <br/> <span class="bg-black text-white px-2">GÜCÜ</span>
                </h2>
                <p class="text-black text-xl font-mono font-bold mb-8 leading-relaxed border-l-4 border-black pl-6 bg-white py-2 border-y-2 md:border-y-0">
                    Düşüncelerini serbest bırak. Haftalık meydan okumalara katıl, topluluğun bir parçası ol ve sınırlarını zorla.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4">
                    <button class="px-8 py-4 bg-black hover:bg-white hover:text-black text-white font-bold border-2 border-transparent hover:border-black transition-all shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_white] hover:shadow-none hover:translate-x-[2px] hover:translate-y-[2px] flex items-center justify-center gap-2 uppercase tracking-wider">
                        <PenTool className="w-5 h-5" /> Yazmaya Başla
                    </button>
                    <button class="px-8 py-4 bg-neo-yellow border-2 border-black text-black font-bold hover:shadow-neo hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all uppercase tracking-wider">
                        Son Yazılar
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Challenge Ticket -->
            <div class="relative group">
                <!-- Background visual -->
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black translate-x-4 translate-y-4 border-2 border-white"></div>
                
                <div class="relative bg-white border-4 border-black p-8 md:p-10 transform transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-8 border-b-4 border-black pb-6">
                        <div>
                            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-neo-teal border-2 border-black text-black text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest block w-fit mb-2 transform -rotate-2">Haftalık Challenge</span>
                            <h3 class="text-4xl font-black text-black mt-3 uppercase italic">"Sessiz Çığlık"</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-neo-yellow border-2 border-black p-2 shadow-neo">
                            <Sparkles className="w-8 h-8 text-black" />
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-black font-bold text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed font-mono">
                        "Hiçbir diyaloğun olmadığı, sadece tasvirlerin konuştuğu bir sahne yaz. Gürültüyü kelimelerinle sustur."
                    </p>

                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 bg-cream border-4 border-black">
                        <div class="flex -space-x-4">
                            {[1,2,3].map(i => (
                                <div class={`w-12 h-12 border-2 border-black bg-white flex items-center justify-center font-black`}>{i}</div>
                            ))}
                            <div class="w-12 h-12 border-2 border-black bg-neo-red flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-black text-white">+42</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-right">
                             <p class="text-xs text-black uppercase font-black mb-1 bg-neo-yellow inline-block px-1">Bitiş</p>
                             <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-black font-mono font-bold text-xl">
                                <Clock className="w-5 h-5" />
                                02:14:59
                             </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
